    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1199843447">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1199843447" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1199843447" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1199843447">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/32277544/">morgan</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">无数次想象初盛唐时长安城的繁荣景象，却毁于藩镇之乱。从此藩镇割据，军阀混战，中央政府无力再集权治国。而长安城也不再是帝国的中心。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1058444780">
        <div class="comment">
